      <div onclick="expand(this)" class="resource-boxes professional">
        <span class="node-label">Professional Resources</span>
        <div class="expanded-content">
          <ul>
            <li class="expandedLI">
              <h2>Psychology Today (Therapist Directory)</h2>
              <h3><a href="https://www.psychologytoday.com/us/therapists">psychologytoday.com</a></h3>
              <h4>
                Use the therapist directory to find licensed therapists, psychologists, and counselors near you. Search by location, specialty, insurance, and more to find the right professional for your needs.
              </h4>
            </li>
            <li class="expandedLI">
              <h2>GoodTherapy</h2>
              <h3><a href="https://www.goodtherapy.org/">goodtherapy.org</a></h3>
              <h4>
                Provides a directory of therapists and counselors, along with articles and resources on various mental health topics. Find professionals who adhere to ethical therapy practices and get support for your mental health journey.
              </h4>
            </li>
            <li class="expandedLI">
              <h2>BetterHelp</h2>
              <h3><a href="https://www.betterhelp.com/">betterhelp.com</a></h3>
              <h4>
                Connect with licensed therapists for professional online counseling services. Schedule sessions through live chat, phone, or video, and receive support from the comfort of your home.
              </h4>
            </li>
            <li class="expandedLI">
              <h2>Talkspace</h2>
              <h3><a href="https://www.talkspace.com/">talkspace.com</a></h3>
              <h4>
                Offers professional online therapy with licensed therapists. Communicate with your therapist via text, audio, or video messaging. Flexible plans available for different needs and budgets.
              </h4>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <span id="bottomMessage">Click anywhere to close</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
