              <h3><a href="https://www.nami.org/Support-Education/Support-Groups">nami.org/Support-Education/Support-Groups</a></h3>
              <h4>
                NAMI offers peer-led support groups for individuals living with mental health conditions and their families. Find local and online groups to connect with others and share experiences.
              </h4>
            </li>
            <li class="expandedLI">
              <h2>Depression and Bipolar Support Alliance (DBSA)</h2>
              <h3><a href="https://www.dbsalliance.org/">dbsalliance.org</a></h3>
